  "governance_notes": "All children preserve Stage 1 semantics and Stage 2 interfaces exactly. ParseCommand has no resource dependencies (pure function). PlaceOrder, CancelOrder, and TrackOrder have global_vars and data_operations synchronized with their internal_leaf_accesses. No data stores are exposed in signatures or call_inputs. Constraints and acceptance criteria are derived from preconditions/postconditions and guarantees.",
  "resource_audit": {
